<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳落山了，小飞虫在门廊后的灯光下飞来飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈把棒球帽戴在凯蒂的头上，说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“空气越来越凉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克把一块抹布系在凯蒂的皮带环上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是干什么的？”凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一会儿就知道了。”卢克说，“你拿桶了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿了。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“手电筒呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有。”凯蒂回答道，“我已经准备好去抓蚯蚓了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别离房子太远了。”妈妈说，“别去太久了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂和卢克走出门廊，走向黑暗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“草都湿了。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那很好。”卢克解释道，“蚯蚓喜欢又冷又湿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的脚趾不喜欢。”凯蒂回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的运动鞋湿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“轻轻地走。”卢克提醒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果它们能感觉到我们的脚步声，就会立刻滑回地里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以为我们得挖蚯蚓。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个方法很难。”卢克回答说，“这是一个简单的方法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们小心地穿过草地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了河边癞蛤蟆的叫声外，什么声音也没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，在这儿停下来。”卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打开你的手电筒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂在草地上来回照着红光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看。”他小声说，“蚯蚓都出来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克是对的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>无论光照到哪里，凯蒂都能看见蚯蚓在草地上闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，好恶心啊。”她小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克看了她一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”凯蒂说，“我是说，哦，真酷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，看我怎么做。”卢克命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他弯下腰，抓住其中一条发光的蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他慢慢地把蚯蚓从洞里拽出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓到了。”卢克说，“这是一条大的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把它放进桶里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你试试看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂在卢克旁边弯下腰，很快发现了一条蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她伸出手去抓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓到了！”她说。她举起手给卢克看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她的手里是空的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它逃走了！”她大喊道，“我的手黏糊糊的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就是你的抹布的用途。”卢克解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“擦干你的手，再试一次。这次，抓它的中间部分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当凯蒂用抹布擦手时，她发现了另一条蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她慢慢地伸出手去，抓住它的中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拽了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它不出来。它还在挺着。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“继续拽。”卢克说，“蚯蚓会累的，然后就会放弃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂又拽了一会儿，直到蚯蚓滑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”她叫道，“我抓到了一条！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”卢克说，“把它扔进桶里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，凯蒂和卢克从后门跑进厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都围坐在桌旁，爷爷在给大家分苹果派。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抓到蚯蚓了！”凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不可以放在家里。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，对。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开后门，把水桶放在门廊上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，在你吃苹果派之前，”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先给卢克看看我们的新小鸡，怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂叹了口气。她想聊聊她的蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来，卢克。”她轻声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂带着表弟走出厨房，上了楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开空房间的门，把他拉到了那个小鸡温箱前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们在这儿。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们很可爱，但是很麻烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你得喂它们，清理它们的臭鸡屎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蚯蚓更有趣。”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是肯定的。”凯蒂表示同意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我们去吃点苹果派吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个蚯蚓猎手没注意到走廊里有另一个猎手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰利一直在黑暗中静静地等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它悄悄地朝空房间走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门只开着一个缝。杰利把一只爪子放在门上推了推。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当门打开时，小鸡们在温箱里叽叽喳喳地叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>